1 - go to the root folder of your project
    cd ~/webroot/obriens
2 - hg pull
3 - hg update 

terminal
4 - hg merge default
    after you need to resolv all conflicts in a terminal mode

phpstorm
4 - Right click on root folder
5 - select mercurial/merge
6 - choose the branch if it is a feature choose develop else (hotfix) choose default
7 - resolve all conflicts
8 - hg commit -m "mergin with [name-of-the-branch]"


